1
00:00:06,543 --> 00:00:07,547
Anybody home?
有人在家吗?

2
00:00:07,939 --> 00:00:08,183
Hi.
你好.

3
00:00:08,615 --> 00:00:10,169
Hi. Hi Danny.
你好.你好Danny.

4
00:00:10,798 --> 00:00:11,465
How you doing. Lisa?
你好吗,Lisa?

5
00:00:14,128 --> 00:00:15,187
I found that video.
我找到那盘录像带了.

6
00:00:17,964 --> 00:00:20,201
"Mars Needs Women". Excellent.
《火星需要女人》.非常好.

7
00:00:21,141 --> 00:00:22,405
I looked everywhere for it,
我到处找这盘带子,

8
00:00:22,764 --> 00:00:24,320
and I finally went to Video King.
最后在"录像大王"店里找到了.

9
00:00:24,977 --> 00:00:26,621
Michael, it is a great store.
Michael, 那是一家很不错的音像店.

10
00:00:26,937 --> 00:00:29,173
Lisa, how long did you live in California?
Lisa,你在California住了多久?

11
00:00:29,690 --> 00:00:31,144
My whole life until college. Why?
上大学之前一直住那儿.为什么?

12
00:00:31,989 --> 00:00:36,089
I don't know. Maybe I should move to L.A.
我不知道.也许我该搬到洛杉矶去.

13
00:00:36,993 --> 00:00:38,097
What? Why?
什么?为什么?

14
00:00:38,418 --> 00:00:40,729
They have an excellent football team.
那里有一直很好的橄榄球队.

15
00:00:41,148 --> 00:00:42,046
You're pathetic.
你真可怜.

16
00:00:42,611 --> 00:00:44,999
Danny, you don't want to live in California.
Danny,你不会想住在California的.

17
00:00:45,417 --> 00:00:46,712
It's one big disaster area.
那是一个充满灾难的地区.

18
00:00:47,358 --> 00:00:49,073
So? So is my life.
那又怎么样?我的生活也是如此.

19
00:00:49,440 --> 00:00:51,719
No. I mean things like floods.
不.我是指洪水之类的灾难.

20
00:00:52,147 --> 00:00:57,580
And if it isn't a flood, it's a fire or an earthquake. Earthquakes, Danny.
如果不发洪水的话,也会有火灾, 或者地震.地震啊,Danny.

21
00:00:58,842 --> 00:00:59,885
Have you ever been in one?
你经历过地震吗?

22
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:00,808
Plenty of times.
很多次了.

23
00:01:01,009 --> 00:01:03,382
Most of them are small; you don't feel them.
大多数都是小地震,你感受不到.

24
00:01:04,094 --> 00:01:05,190
But the one in 1990?
但1990年的那一次?

25
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:08,369
I was going into the airport and the ground started to move.
我正走进机场时, 大地开始震动.

26
00:01:08,893 --> 00:01:11,528
People didn't want to stay in the airport, obviously,
人们不想待在机场里, 当然了,

27
00:01:11,696 --> 00:01:14,738
so they started running out of it, crying and screaming.
所以他们往机场外跑, 哭泣着, 尖叫着.

28
00:01:15,404 --> 00:01:16,396
So?
那又怎么样呢?

29
00:01:18,125 --> 00:01:21,090
The only disasters we have in New England are blizzards.
在新英格兰我们唯一的灾难是暴风雪.

30
00:01:22,086 --> 00:01:22,970
And hurricanes.
还有飓风.

31
00:01:23,368 --> 00:01:24,697
And hurricanes.
还有飓风.

32
00:01:24,905 --> 00:01:26,116
And Danny's love life.
还有Danny的爱情生活.

33
00:01:26,465 --> 00:01:28,995
Danny. Did you and Jeannette break up?
Danny.你和Jeannette分手了吗?

34
00:01:29,589 --> 00:01:32,604
Yep. I dropped her like a hot potato.
是的.我像扔烫手山芋一样把她甩了.

35
00:01:32,952 --> 00:01:35,063
"Typhoon Danny and his Storm of Love", 
《台风Danny和他的爱情风暴》.

36
00:01:35,329 --> 00:01:37,181
a new film by Michael Chung.
Michael Chung的新影片.

37
00:01:37,489 --> 00:01:38,288
I like it.
我喜欢这个想法.

38
00:01:38,492 --> 00:01:41,553
Yeah, well, I'm charging you a fortune for the rights.
Yeah, well,那我可要向你收一大笔版权费.

